{
  "stem": "13251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I mean, I was there for, for, on a trial basis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was, like I said, something I always wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was totally excited about it and, and loved that school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was the only school that I really loved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the others, you know, there's some things I like, some things I didn't like.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nothing about the school I didn't like, even the fact that I had to take maybe two buses and, and a subway in order to get there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, as long as, as long as I was allowed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, they took me there on, as I said, trial basis, and at the end of three months-- I, I don't know if it was three months or four.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the first term I was called in by the principal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In England, they call them the headmaster.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said he was, you know, that I-- it was OK for me to stay, that I have progressed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, I have a letter from him I, I just discovered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know I had it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I have-- written by him as a, as a recommendation, a real good letter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What happened was I had this scholarship, and I was torn between making a decision when I was, when I was notified by the Youth Aliyah that I can go to-- immigrate to Israel.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when I first was told about it I, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't respond positive because I just started my art training, and I, I can always go to Israel later, I thought.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then they came back with me with this story, that my brother was 17, and if we wait another year, he'll be 18.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
